        <p class='text-muted-foreground'>
          To create a new project, click on the "New Project" button in the left
          sidebar. You'll be prompted to enter your project name and
          description. Once created, you can start exploring AI-generated ideas,
          developing your business model, and building your startup strategy
          using our various tools.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ 3 -->
