        <p class='text-muted-foreground'>
          Our AI assistant uses advanced machine learning models to analyze your
          project requirements and provide tailored recommendations. Simply
          describe your idea or ask specific questions, and our AI will generate
          insights, suggest improvements, and help you build various aspects of
          your business including business models, financial projections,
          marketing strategies, and team building.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ 4 -->
      <div class='border-b border-border pb-4'>
        <h3 class='text-lg font-medium text-foreground mb-2'>What are credits
          and how do they work?</h3>
        <p class='text-muted-foreground'>
          Credits are used to access premium AI features and generate detailed
          reports. Each AI interaction consumes a certain number of credits. You
          can purchase additional credits from your account dashboard when your
          balance runs low. Different features consume different amounts of
          credits.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ 5 -->
      <div class='border-b border-border pb-4'>
        <h3 class='text-lg font-medium text-foreground mb-2'>How do I export my
          business plan?</h3>
        <p class='text-muted-foreground'>
          Once you've completed your business plan using our tools, navigate to
          the "Business Plan" section in your project. Look for the "Export"
          button, which allows you to download your plan as a PDF, Word
          document, or other available formats. You can customize the content
          before exporting to suit your specific needs.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ 6 -->
      <div class='border-b border-border pb-4'>
        <h3 class='text-lg font-medium text-foreground mb-2'>Can I collaborate
          with team members?</h3>
        <p class='text-muted-foreground'>
          Yes! Our platform supports team collaboration. In your project
          settings, you can invite team members by email. Each team member will
          have access to the project based on their assigned permissions. You
          can manage access levels and permissions in the team management
          section.
        </p>
